        <div class="mask">

            <div class="sectionY"> <span></span>
                <h1> Join </h1>
            </div>
            <div class="sectionX" id="join">
                <p> No need for email or phone number or any personal info to create an account, you just need to enter
                    any username and any password and pincode of four-numbers. </p>
                <p> No one will see your data except you. your data will be saved in front-end in your side not in the
                    server, that means you have to save your data in a private file each time you enter or exit the app,
                    and
                    if you don't save it you will lose your data. </p>

                <div class="space">
                    <h2>username and password</h2>
                    <p> Please note that you can't change the username or the password or the pincode after you enter.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sectionY"> <span></span>
                <h1> Chat with a random person or group </h1>
            </div>
            <div class="sectionX" id="randomly">
                <p>Search for a random person or group, and your data and everything will be
                    secret and no one will see or save your data except you. </p>
